commitResults.messageBody:
Person Class as well as different identity and data fields were present.

To support functionalities unique to RC4HDB, more classes are required, including Resident, Room, Gender, House, MatricNumber.

Let's create these classes, then look towards shifting the internal implementation of RC4HDB from Person to Resident.
